title: Walt Disney Best Comics - Mickey Mouse
description:
'Walt Disney Best Comics - Mickey Mouse'

Abbeville Press, 1978, 207 pages (this version)

This collection was edited and includes an introduction by Floyd Gottfredson. It contains eleven stories that he worked on between 1930 and 1937. Unlike the previous two Fantagraphics Mickey Mouse books that were uploaded, all of the stories in this book are colored.
